    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Teudebertus/Cillo">Teuperto, que
                            Cillo</name></persName> vocatur, filio <persName><name ref="Ilderada"
                                >Ilderade</name></persName> riceve da <persName ref="#people/214"
                            key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>, gratia Dei huius sancte Lucane
                        ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>, per cartula livellario
                        nomine (…), duo petie de terra, quod sunt vinee, et una petia de terra quod
                        est oliveto in loco et finibus <placeName ref="#places/180"
                            >Vaccule</placeName>, pertenentes <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/242"
                            key="#Churches"><rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> Sancti Petri, sito
                            foras <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Cities">civitate ista
                                Lucense</placeName></orgName>, qui est de suppotestate ipsius <rs
                            key="#Mother_churches">epischopatui</rs> vestro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>; qui una ex ipse petia de vinea <rs key="#Confinia"
                            >uno capo tenet</rs> in vinea <persName key="#Confinia"><name
                                ref="Uirinus">Vuarini</name></persName>, et alio capo tenet in terra
                            <persName key="#Confinia"><name ref="Leo">Lei</name></persName>, lato
                        uno tenet in terra <orgName key="#Confinia #Churches #Monasteries"><rs
                                key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                            <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs> Sancti Angeli</orgName>, et alio
                        lato tenet in simitula et aliquantulo in terra <persName key="#Confinia"
                                ><name ref="Cuneradus">Chuneradi</name></persName>; et ille alia
                        petia de vinea <rs key="#Confinia">uno capo tenet</rs> in <rs key="#Roads"
                            >via</rs>, alio capo tene in <rs key="#Mountains">monte</rs>, lato uno
                        tenet in terra <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/226" key="#Confinia">Sancti
                            Laurentii</orgName>, et alio lato tene in terra qui fuit <persName
                            key="#Confinia">quondam <name ref="Philippus">Filipi</name></persName>;
                        et ille tertia petia de terra quod est oliveto uno capo tenet in <rs
                            key="#Mountains">monte</rs>, et alio capo tenet in suprascripta <rs
                            key="#Roads">via</rs>, lato uno tenet in terra de filii <persName
                            key="#Confinia">quondam <name ref="Auderamus"
                        >Auderami</name></persName>, et alio lato tenet in terra predicte <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/226" key="#Confinia #Churches">Sancti
                            Laurentii</orgName>; suprascripte duo petie de terra quod sunt vinee et
                        denominata petia quod est oliveto qualiter ab omnis partes circumdate sunt
                        per designatas locas cum cesis et omnibus arboribus suis in integrum mihi
                        eas dedisti tali ordinem ut in mea vel de meis heredes sint potestatem
                        abendi, inperandi, laborare faciendi, meliorandi et nobis privato nomine
                        usufructuandi (…). Censo: pro omni censum et iustitiam exinde tibi vel ad
                        sucessoribus tuis ad pars predicte ecclesie Sancti Petri per singulos annos,
                        in mense ianuario, reddere debeamus per nos aut per misso nostro vobis vel
                        ad locoposito illo, qui pre tempore in ipsa ecclesia Sancti Petri fuerit,
                        aut in ipsa ecclesia mittantur, argentum denarios bonos expendiviles numero
                        quatraginta et octo tantum (…). Pena: spondeo ego qui supra Teuperto una cum
                        meis heredes conponere tibi (…) penam argentum soledos quatraginta (…).
                            <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Petrus"
                            >Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Cities #Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>. </ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Andreas">Andreas</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Notary"><name
                                ref="Georgius">Georgius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Roppaldus">Roppaldus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Ragifunsus"
                            >Rachifonsus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ermipertus">Ermiperto</name></persName>,<persName
                            key="#Witness #Archpriests"><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Archpriests">archipresbiter</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Teudaldus">Teudaldu</name></persName></ab>
                </div>
